                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": "<ul class=\"info\">\n<li>\n<div class=\"label\">Onderwerp</div>\n<div class=\"value\">Champagne</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div class=\"label\">Schooltype</div>\n<div class=\"value\">VMBO</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div class=\"label\">Doelgroep</div>\n<div class=\"value\">Niveau 3 &amp; 4</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div class=\"label\">Vakgebieden</div>\n<div class=\"value\">Horeca</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div class=\"label\">Aantal personen</div>\n<div class=\"value\">5 leerlingen</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div class=\"label\">Totale tijd</div>\n<div class=\"value\">3 tot 5 klokuren</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"intro\">Het vinificatie proces van Champagne.</p>\n"
                }
            ],
            "sections": [
                {
                    "reference": {
                        "value": "186329"
                    },
                    "heading": {
                        "type": "heading",
                        "content": "1. Inleiding",
                        "level": 2
                    },
                    "items": [
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": "<div class=\"freeformat\">\n<p><strong><span><span>Deze site gaat over het proces wat de druif uit de Champagnestreek moet ondergaan om te komen tot wat men ook wel de \"Goden drank\" noemt</span>.</span></strong> </p>\n<p><img title=\"de streek\" src=\"http://mediaprovider.wm.kennisnet.nl/MediaProvider/img/11880337.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"541\"/></p>\n</div>\n<p>?</p>\n"
                        }
                    ],
                    "sections": []
                },
                {
                    "reference": {
                        "value": "186330"
                    },
                    "heading": {
                        "type": "heading",
                        "content": "2. Taak",
                        "level": 2
                    },
                    "items": [
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": "<p>Wij gaan op zoek naar informatie over het vinificatie proces van Champagne.</p>\n<p>Wij doen dit in de volgende stappen:</p>\n<p>1 De Druivenrassen</p>\n<p> </p>\n<div class=\"O text-align-center\"><span><a onclick=\"function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; window.event.cancelBubble=true;&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }\" href=\"http://nl.wikipedia.org/wiki/pinot_meunier\" target=\"_parent\"><span style=\"color:#ccccff;\">Pinot meunier</span></a></span></div>\n<p>                                      <span><a onclick=\"function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; window.event.cancelBubble=true;&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }\" href=\"http://nl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chardonnay\" target=\"_parent\"><span style=\"color:#ccccff;\">Chardonnay</span></a></span></p>\n<div class=\"O text-align-center\"><span><a onclick=\"function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; window.event.cancelBubble=true;&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }\" href=\"http://nl.wikipedia.org/wiki/pinot_noir\" target=\"_parent\"><span style=\"color:#ccccff;\">Pinot noir</span></a></span></div>\n<p>2 De Champagnestreek</p>\n<ol>\n<li>ligging</li>\n<li>klimmaat</li>\n<li>gromdsoort</li>\n</ol>\n<p>3 Het Vinificatieproces</p>\n<ol>\n<li>smaken</li>\n<li>het proces</li>\n<li>type Champagne</li>\n</ol>\n<p>4 Het uitschenken</p>\n<p>5 Het bewaren</p>\n<p>?</p>\n"
                        }
                    ],
                    "sections": []
                },
                {
                    "reference": {
                        "value": "186331"
                    },
                    "heading": {
                        "type": "heading",
                        "content": "3. Werkwijze",
                        "level": 2
                    },
                    "items": [
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": "<p>In de Champagne zijn slechts drie druivenrassen toegestaan namelijk de:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Pinot meunier</li>\n<li>Pinot noir</li>\n<li>chardonnay</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Opdracht 1</strong></p>\n<p>Bestudeer onderstaande links en lees in je drankenkennisboek op blz. 126 alles over de eigenschappen van die druivenrassen</p>\n<p><a onclick=\"function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; window.event.cancelBubble=true;&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }\" href=\"http://nl.wikipedia.org/wiki/pinot_meunier\" target=\"_parent\"><span style=\"color:#ccccff;\">Pinot meunier </span></a>                                      <span><a onclick=\"function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; window.event.cancelBubble=true;&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }\" href=\"http://nl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chardonnay\" target=\"_parent\"><span style=\"color:#ccccff;\">Chardonnay</span></a></span></p>\n<div class=\"O text-align-center\"><span><a onclick=\"function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; window.event.cancelBubble=true;&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }\" href=\"http://nl.wikipedia.org/wiki/pinot_noir\" target=\"_parent\"><span style=\"color:#ccccff;\">Pinot noir</span></a></span></div>\n<div class=\"O text-align-center\"> </div>\n<div class=\"O text-align-center\"><span>Geef van alle drie de soorten een duidelijke karakter omschrijving.</span></div>\n<div class=\"O text-align-center\"> </div>\n<div class=\"O text-align-center\"> </div>\n<div class=\"O text-align-center\"> </div>\n<div class=\"O text-align-center\"><span><img title=\"pinot noir\" src=\"http://mediaprovider.wm.kennisnet.nl/MediaProvider/img/11898562.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"78\" height=\"117\"/></span></div>\n<div class=\"O text-align-center\"> </div>\n<div class=\"O text-align-center\"><span><img title=\"chardonnay\" src=\"http://mediaprovider.wm.kennisnet.nl/MediaProvider/img/11898566.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"116\" height=\"113\"/></span></div>\n<div class=\"O text-align-center\"> </div>\n<div class=\"O text-align-center\"> </div>\n<p><span><strong>Opdracht 2</strong></span></p>\n<p><span>Omschrijf  de ligging, de grondsoort en het klimaat in de Champagne</span></p>\n<p><span>(blz 126 pragraaf 10.3 , drankenkennis)</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span><strong>Opdracht 3</strong></span></p>\n<p><span>Maak een korte samenvatting van het vinificatieproces en geef in het kort de stappen weer.</span></p>\n<p><span>stappen: 1 pluk</span></p>\n<p><span>             2 persen</span></p>\n<p><span>             3 alcoholische gisting van de <span class=\"font-size-10pt\"><a onclick=\"function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; window.event.cancelBubble=true;&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }\" href=\"http://nl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Most_%28oenologie%29\" target=\"_parent\"><span style=\"color:#b2b2b2;\">most</span></a></span><span class=\"font-size-10pt\"> </span></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-10pt\">             <span class=\"font-size-small\">4 oversteek-mengen van wijn</span></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-10pt font-size-small\">             5 toevoeging van  de liqueur de tirage</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-10pt font-size-small\">             6 bottelen-2e gisting op de fles</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-10pt\">         <span class=\"font-size-20pt\"><a onclick=\"function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; window.event.cancelBubble=true;&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }\" href=\"http://users.telenet.be/lucsteurs/remuage.htm\" target=\"_parent\"><span style=\"color:#ccccff;\">Remuage</span></a></span><span class=\"font-size-20pt\"> </span></span></p>\n<p> <span class=\"font-size-20pt font-size-small\">            7 degorgement,toevoeging van liqueur d'expedition</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-20pt font-size-small\">             8 nieuwe kurk en muskelet</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-20pt font-size-small\"><strong>Opdracht 4</strong></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-20pt font-size-small\">Beschrijf nu de vijf basis smaken van Champagne</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-20pt font-size-small\">1. extra brut</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-20pt font-size-small\">2. brut</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-20pt font-size-small\">3. extra sec</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-20pt font-size-small\">4. demi sec</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-20pt font-size-small\">5. doux.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-20pt font-size-small\"><strong>Opdracht 5</strong></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-20pt font-size-small\">Het uitschenken van champagne:</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-20pt font-size-small\">Bekijk eerst dit filmpje;  <a onclick=\"function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; window.event.cancelBubble=true;&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }\" href=\"http://www.pczapper.tv/pzc5/lfui/?v=2465938\" target=\"_parent\"><span class=\"font-size-x-large\" style=\"color:#ccccff;\">filmpje</span></a></span></p>\n<p>Lees nu blz. 128 paragraaf: openen van mousserende wijnen uit het drankenkennisboek. en zet; </p>\n<div class=\"O text-align-center\"><span class=\"font-size-20pt\"><a onclick=\"function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; function anonymous()&#13; {&#13; window.event.cancelBubble=true;&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }&#13; }\" href=\"http://home.scarlet.be/be031330/ontkurken.htm\" target=\"_parent\"><span style=\"color:#ccccff;\">Alle regels op een rijtje!</span></a></span></div>\n<div class=\"O text-align-center\">\n<div class=\"text-align-center\"><strong>Tot slot:</strong></div>\n<div class=\"text-align-center\">Beschrijf in een paar regels hoe Champagne bewaard wordt en in welke omstandigheden.</div>\n<div class=\"text-align-center\">veel succes</div>\n</div>\n<p>?</p>\n"
                        }
                    ],
                    "sections": []
                },
                {
                    "reference": {
